Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.48,0:00:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飘忽不定的罪孽之影
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.35,0:00:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可悲的宿命 迷失的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.79,0:00:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因憎恨和被憎恨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.11,0:00:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而破碎的两面镜子 是双重的枷锁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.07,0:00:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在交错的时光与黑暗中浮现
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.48,0:00:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的怨恨 替你消除
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.56,0:02:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.23,0:02:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大碗拉面 让您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.44,0:02:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,修一 可以走了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.75,0:02:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 那么等我收拾完
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.60,0:02:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行了 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.28,0:02:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不然就错过探望时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.47,0:02:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.84,0:02:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.02,0:03:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也给千波带些饺子去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.47,0:03:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那里的那些
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.32,0:03:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 她一定会喜欢的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.59,0:03:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好 八木泽先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.08,0:03:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.25,0:03:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夫人在等你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.11,0:03:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.53,0:03:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个是老板给的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.23,0:03:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偷偷吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.17,0:03:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是饺子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.74,0:03:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,闻出来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.35,0:03:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,修
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.91,0:03:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想住到六人的病房去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.99,0:04:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个人总是容易乱想
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.78,0:04:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在六人间的话还能交朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.06,0:04:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,千波
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.57,0:04:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道要什么时候才可以出院
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.13,0:04:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,寂寞的话可以让学生时代的朋友来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.62,0:04:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比如那个和你很要好的恭子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.52,0:04:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们很久没见了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.35,0:04:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,修
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.61,0:04:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我来联络好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.19,0:04:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有电话号码吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.09,0:04:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想见别的朋友的话都交给我来联系好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.33,0:04:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说谎了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.51,0:04:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说什么中了彩票
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.65,0:04:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要勉强啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.10,0:04:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这病房那么贵的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.32,0:04:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没有说谎 真的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.53,0:04:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别瞎担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.59,0:04:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,千波
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.47,0:04:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对不起 我走神了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.36,0:04:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.25,0:04:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.66,0:04:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.85,0:05:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 修 和我说好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.64,0:05:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不论发生什么都不要怨恨别人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.59,0:05:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么呀 为什么说这个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.61,0:05:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为你看上去很不安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.98,0:05:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稍微有点担心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.57,0:05:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.85,0:05:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是有点累了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.76,0:05:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会做让千波担心的事的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.48,0:05:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的运气来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.27,0:05:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最近是好事不断
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.22,0:05:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以 千波的病也会好起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.17,0:05:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.45,0:05:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.48,0:06:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都已经一个小时了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.47,0:06:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底还要等多久啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.57,0:06:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.30,0:06:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,客人都不愿让我走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.17,0:06:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.08,0:06:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是看到了杂志上的招聘广告才
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.88,0:06:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,石本连是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.16,0:06:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,长得还不错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.68,0:06:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.76,0:06:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想进我们店工作的 每天都有100个人左右呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.32,0:06:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过那些人长的实在不咋的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.86,0:06:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像你这样的很久没有遇到过了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.01,0:06:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能每天都有100人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.60,0:06:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一次接触这行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.74,0:06:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.70,0:06:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不容易嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.17,0:06:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我现在是个的一流老板
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.00,0:07:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但半年前只是个名不见经传的小牛郎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.93,0:07:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,定额的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.59,0:07:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开始的三个月是50万
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.72,0:07:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以后是80万
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.45,0:07:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不到的话要罚钱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.25,0:07:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不是说没有定额的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.72,0:07:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,连
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.90,0:07:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么相信别人最好不要干牛郎了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.84,0:07:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有详细的都写在这上了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.84,0:07:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回去后好好看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.32,0:07:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,写得是白痴都能看懂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.49,0:07:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.46,0:07:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和传闻中一样讨厌的家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.78,0:07:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用调查了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.38,0:08:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.29,0:08:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 已经好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.32,0:08:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.86,0:08:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.48,0:08:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听好了 就借这一次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.66,0:08:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太感谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.84,0:08:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,半年之内我一定还
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.05,0:08:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他真是会勉强自己啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.25,0:08:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,据说现在他连高利贷都借不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.72,0:08:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每天都在求朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.85,0:08:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算是为了深爱的妻子也稍微过火了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.94,0:08:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先不说好坏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.17,0:08:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要拿到那笔钱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.98,0:08:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs35}（友情提示 3人是破坏ATM机的ATM强盗）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.72,0:08:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.06,0:08:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别命令我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.69,0:08:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 不要发呆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.64,0:09:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那事发生不久前
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.50,0:09:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,翔贵被他原来所在的牛郎俱乐部开除了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.00,0:09:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原因是他想用诡计来争头牌的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.81,0:09:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候翔贵发过誓
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.05,0:09:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定要让那些赶自己出去的人后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.31,0:09:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后仿佛命运的捉弄般
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.55,0:09:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们相遇了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.59,0:09:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像有2千万吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.72,0:09:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还真不少
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.47,0:09:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 我们分钱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.03,0:09:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行 现在还不能分
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.02,0:09:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要先把钱藏起来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.93,0:09:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.99,0:09:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,藏起来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.28,0:09:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别说傻话了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.29,0:09:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在用的话会立刻就被发现的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.28,0:09:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等风声平了再说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.60,0:10:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忍耐一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.74,0:10:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我又不是马上用掉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.32,0:10:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.14,0:10:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,逃到国外就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.94,0:10:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像电视里那样就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.52,0:10:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,远走高飞的人也不会被抓枪毙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.86,0:10:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.96,0:10:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干掉他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.14,0:10:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.65,0:10:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.57,0:10:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.37,0:10:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么是我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.36,0:10:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干吧 不然不给你钱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.03,0:10:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把你也杀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.60,0:10:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你死了的话你的妻子会怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.25,0:10:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,背负着你欠的债
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.70,0:10:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一边跟没把握治好的病魔斗争
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.38,0:10:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不活下去可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.67,0:10:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你为你妻子所做的一切最终成为了她痛苦的根源
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.93,0:10:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样也可以吗 八木泽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.76,0:11:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八木泽杀了佐久间
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.05,0:11:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 他没有得到钱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.78,0:11:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,报警的话自己也会被抓
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.48,0:11:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是杀人犯的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.90,0:11:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说八木泽被那个牛郎漂亮地骗了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.51,0:11:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不论发生什么都不要怨恨别人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.67,0:11:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.30,0:11:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做好了吗 爱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.24,0:11:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.43,0:11:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个孩子能喜欢的话就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.82,0:11:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有信件送到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.67,0:12:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 千波
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.79,0:12:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地狱少女
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.89,0:12:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你终于决定了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.31,0:12:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一目连
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.47,0:12:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK 小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.58,0:12:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.66,0:12:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你若真的要消除怨恨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.52,0:12:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将那红线解开即可
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.69,0:12:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,解开绳线 就和我正式缔结了契约
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.18,0:12:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怨恨的人将立刻坠入地狱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.47,0:12:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下地狱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.30,0:12:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.14,0:12:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怨恨若已消除 你自己也要付出代价
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.12,0:13:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,害人终害己
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.63,0:13:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,缔结契约之后
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.38,0:13:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的灵魂也将堕入地狱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.25,0:13:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也？是马上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.53,0:13:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是在你死之后了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.31,0:13:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.68,0:13:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死了以后啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.47,0:13:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.41,0:13:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我理所应当下地狱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.60,0:13:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.00,0:13:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会留下千波自己先走的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.12,0:13:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么 解开吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.52,0:13:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是现在解开
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.07,0:13:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还有事没完成
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.93,0:13:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正都要下地狱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.85,0:13:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好喝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.00,0:13:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是哪里来的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.04,0:13:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.15,0:13:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是八木泽先生他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.12,0:13:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小菊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.33,0:13:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也给花儿喝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.86,0:13:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.32,0:14:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.13,0:14:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说要自首？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.57,0:14:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.29,0:14:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都到如今了这是为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.96,0:14:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,钱？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.29,0:14:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是明白人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.16,0:14:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只要自己应得的那份
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.51,0:14:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没钱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.65,0:14:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不想被捕就去准备
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.86,0:14:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你忘了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.26,0:14:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你被捕的话你的妻子怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.22,0:14:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别再吓唬我了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.78,0:14:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去 不自首也只是等着身败名裂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.49,0:14:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你打算奋不顾身吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.39,0:14:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日落之前把钱准备好到这里来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.24,0:14:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日落还不来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.35,0:14:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就立刻去自首
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.64,0:14:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快去准备 你没剩多少时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.96,0:14:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.38,0:15:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好喝哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.20,0:15:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要喝的话别客气
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.61,0:15:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.84,0:15:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来是修一啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.97,0:15:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  今天不是休息吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.21,0:15:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 但是日落之前找不到事做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.89,0:15:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.08,0:15:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那真是麻烦你帮忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.90,0:15:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都堆了这么多了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.02,0:15:49.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我来洗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.33,0:15:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.98,0:15:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,千波怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.18,0:15:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,托你的福 病情已经稳定了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.66,0:16:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像这样的话不久应该就可以出院了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.22,0:16:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 那样的话再好不过了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.03,0:16:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上天一定在好好看着你们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.59,0:16:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以说 像你这样老实勤奋的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.26,0:16:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会遇到不幸的事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.86,0:16:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说的是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.99,0:16:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,千波能出院的话真的是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.21,0:16:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦增多的话只会劳烦小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.55,0:16:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要尿尿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.87,0:16:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,带我去厕所 阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.09,0:16:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.31,0:16:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一个人去好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.13,0:16:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,厕所我不认识
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.92,0:16:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道…你这孩子真是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.20,0:17:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要撒尿 我要撒尿 我要撒尿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.01,0:17:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0054,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.50,0:17:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还没来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.90,0:17:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,千波
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.50,0:17:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朋友？谁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.05,0:17:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你人真是太老实了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.55,0:17:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,千波
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.92,0:17:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.67,0:17:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来得正好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.07,0:17:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们刚好说完
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.46,0:17:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说完…难道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.40,0:17:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.15,0:17:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,千波
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.08,0:17:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.49,0:17:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿修你真的杀人了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.40,0:17:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她说不要那个钱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.33,0:17:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那种杀人得到的钱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.60,0:17:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.05,0:17:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.57,0:17:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 千波
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.13,0:18:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没有杀过人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.03,0:18:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杀过 我明明亲眼看见的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.00,0:18:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.98,0:18:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用铁管用力打下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.78,0:18:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种野蛮的事你也做的出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.82,0:18:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,千波
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.72,0:18:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.52,0:18:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别碰到我 杀人犯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.19,0:18:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真脏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.93,0:18:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.58,0:18:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,千波
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.89,0:18:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 这下事情大了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.69,0:18:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫护士
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.99,0:18:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我保证以后不会再出现在我面前
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.82,0:18:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.04,0:18:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的人生里没有你的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.38,0:18:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别说这些了 叫护士
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.36,0:19:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你先保证
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.71,0:19:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫护士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.74,0:19:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,断掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.17,0:19:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.31,0:19:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早知道会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.14,0:19:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早知道会这样 那个时候我就应该解开的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.05,0:19:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怨恨已闻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.40,0:19:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.96,0:19:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.75,0:19:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好 久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.78,0:19:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,连 那家伙跟我搭讪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.03,0:20:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 就凭那种脸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.00,0:20:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌 那脸是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.40,0:20:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.15,0:20:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都比你帅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.60,0:20:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 你们到底在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.89,0:20:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的脸很奇怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.09,0:20:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.20,0:20:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.67,0:20:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,脸 我的脸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.51,0:20:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迷途于黑暗的可悲阴影
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.26,0:20:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伤害 鄙视他人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.65,0:20:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沉溺于罪恶的孽魂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.78,0:20:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来死一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.39,0:20:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.08,0:20:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以把手伸进去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.55,0:21:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好深好深
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.12,0:21:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这份怨恨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.77,0:21:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将流向地狱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.76,0:21:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让她安静一会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.01,0:21:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十分感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.28,0:21:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事真的太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.49,0:21:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有欲望的话 就不会有这种结局
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.72,0:21:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是人类啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.27,0:21:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对吧 小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.33,0:21:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.56,0:21:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你是那个时候的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.89,0:21:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是人类吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.41,0:21:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.01,0:21:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.11,0:22:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说 你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.61,0:22:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.81,0:22:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小姐好不容易给你做的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.33,0:22:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坏掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.19,0:22:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.44,0:22:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会努力把债务还清的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.14,0:22:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好起来的话我就去自首
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.30,0:22:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以请原谅我 千波
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.63,0:22:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,千波 已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.85,0:22:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肚子饿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.12,0:22:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.73,0:22:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 请问你有见过我女儿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.60,0:22:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的怨恨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.40,0:23:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,替你消除
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.93,0:24:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名字
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.04,0:24:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,丽音
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.03,0:24:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,山田丽音
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.66,0:24:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么怨恨吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.75,0:24:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能不恨
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.65,0:24:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前辈那家伙 让人太不爽了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.77,0:24:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.48,0:24:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你自己也会下地狱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.06,0:24:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓 只要把他送进地狱就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.61,0:24:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.67,0:24:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怨恨已闻
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.30,0:24:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.71,0:25:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奔向地狱的暴走
